message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with signal processing and audio analysis. Other likely categories could be cs.CL (computational linguistics) as the paper deals with detecting and separating singing voice, which involves language processing, cs.LG (machine learning) as the paper proposes a multi-task learning approach, cs.CV (computer vision) as the paper deals with identifying biases in datasets, and cs.MM (multimedia) as the paper deals with music processing.
